export function Aside({ chosenAnime }) { console.log(chosenAnime); const producers = chosenAnime?.producers ?.map((el) => el) ?.map((el) => el?.name) ?.join(" , "); const licensors = chosenAnime?.licensors ?.map((el) => el) ?.map((el) => el?.name) ?.join(" , "); const studios = chosenAnime?.studios ?.map((el) => el) ?.map((el) => el?.name) ?.join(" , "); const themes = chosenAnime?.themes ?.map((el) => el) ?.map((el) => el?.name) ?.join(" , "); const demographics = chosenAnime?.demographics ?.map((el) => el) ?.map((el) => el?.name) ?.join(" , "); console.log(studios); return (
Title: {chosenAnime?.title}
Type: {chosenAnime?.type}
Episodes: {chosenAnime?.episodes}
Status: {chosenAnime?.status}
Aired: {chosenAnime?.aired?.string}
{/*
Premiered: {chosenAnime?.pr}
*/}
Producers: {producers}
Licensors:{licensors}
Studios: {studios}
Source: {chosenAnime?.source}
Theme: {themes}
Demographic: {demographics}
Duration: {chosenAnime?.duration}
Rating: {chosenAnime?.rating}
); }
